---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #d35400;
      --bg: #fff8f0;
      --text: #333;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
    }
    header img {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    header p {
      margin: 0;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    section {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h2 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
  <header>
    <img src="/favicon.png" alt="Logo" loading="lazy" />
    <h1>About Welcome Sweets</h1>
    <p>Our story and values</p>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Founded in 2010, Welcome Sweets started as a small home-based kitchen with a passion for traditional Indian sweets. Over the years, we have grown into a beloved sweet shop known for quality, hygiene, and authentic flavors.</p>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>To bring joy to every celebration with sweets made from the finest ingredients, prepared with love and care.</p>
    <h2>Quality & Hygiene</h2>
    <p>We follow strict hygiene standards, use fresh ingredients, and prepare everything in a clean kitchen environment.</p>
    <h2>Community</h2>
    <p>We love giving back to the community by sponsoring local events and distributing sweets to those in need during festivals.</p>
  </section>
  <section>
    <a href="/" class="btn">← Back to Home</a>
  </section>
</Layout>